title: A review of Episode 1193 Shane Dorian
description:
Shane is a big wave surfer and an avid bow hunter. He's a long time friend of Joe's and is really a fascinating guy to listen to. If you want to learn about what it takes to tackle waves that will most likely kill you check it out lol. Or just listen for fun.

Enjoy the review folks!
